{"tid":2252827,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"點解lf2 唔出手機版","createTime":"2020-10-21T17:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T18:11:52.000Z","uid":57308,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2206bea9b1a3f5ea8ed55fdbf163e3aa5c9fb989","tid":2252827,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:33:36.000Z","msg":"個版權喺邊個到<br />\n應該唔難整<br />\n課金抽下skin咁應該幾好搵？"},{"pid":"0bed791e478f1e02a2eebaed296f7a7a8d3d4bbb","tid":2252827,"uid":38540,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:36:49.000Z","msg":"經典童年回憶LF2移植作！《Hero Fighter》曝光！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gameapps.hk/news/10381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gameapps.hk%2Fnews%2F10381&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPdxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=c1807faa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gameapps.hk/news/10381</a><br />\n<br />\n此POST議員"},{"pid":"1da3705768b4157cc59af2406a2d8c7ac25bc3e1","tid":2252827,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6MdQVGU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6MdQVGU.jpg&h=7d507aff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9ba8a4a08360eb64e7fede7e12b586d4943cb4c","tid":2252827,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0bed791e478f1e02a2eebaed296f7a7a8d3d4bbb","tid":2252827,"uid":38540,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:36:49.000Z","msg":"經典童年回憶LF2移植作！《Hero Fighter》曝光！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gameapps.hk/news/10381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gameapps.hk%2Fnews%2F10381&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPdxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=c1807faa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gameapps.hk/news/10381</a><br />\n<br />\n此POST議員"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:37:50.000Z","msg":"=.="},{"pid":"ee4ab47a551aaf0597a775329bd30234cdf299e0","tid":2252827,"uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:40:20.000Z","msg":"沒有穩定收入，沒有團隊，只有一個人在家裏獨自做開發。這七年，一點也不容易走。小熊每天十點起床，一做便是做到凌晨二，三點，星期一至日也在工作。因為只有一個人，從人物設計，圖像設計，遊戲開發，調試，影片剪接等等全是小熊一個人包辦。「我覺得自己在這創業路上好像一隻烏龜，走得很慢很慢，好 像沒有什麼出路卻還不放棄，全憑一股傻勁堅持到現在。」<br />\n<br />\n大概在 09 到 10 年，電腦板的英雄大作戰面世，為小熊帶來一些收入。只是好景不常，遊戲很快便被中國破解團隊破解了，能讓玩家免費任玩。收入頓時變成零，小熊坦言心情直跌落谷底。<br />\n<br />\n「那時候我足足沮喪了兩年，成個人變得好摺，在家裏不想外出和人溝通。」<br />\n<br />\n「還記得有一次我看見一本雜誌在介紹我的遊戲，我興高采烈地翻開，怎料第一頁便是教人如何破解我的遊戲，免費下載來玩，讓我感到很心酸。」<br />\n<br />\n「係香港做Indie（獨立遊戲開發者）其實好慘，好多時別人會覺得你不腳踏實地，見工時公司甚至會不把它當成經驗，還會壓低你人工，覺得自己請你是在拯救你。反而在外國，Indie的經驗會受到尊重，即使你創業失敗的代價在外國也會低一點。」<br />\n<br />\n兩年前，小熊把心一橫，決定為遊戲推出手機版，作最後嘗試。英雄大作戰X剛在本月初上架，短短三星期已有超過60萬人下載。雖然付費玩家並不多，但卻給了小熊信心和希望。<br />\n<br />\n「現時在支那和香港的遊戲，大都參照外國成功的遊戲，改改圖畫於短時間內發行，埋沒了許多原創idea。我的夢想，則是創造一隻結合支那歷史，格鬥和即時戰略的遊戲，並把它由香港帶到全世界。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2015/07/06/little-fighter-creator-interview/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2015%2F07%2F06%2Flittle-fighter-creator-interview%2F&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPdxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=09c3d285\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2015/07/06/little-fighter-creator-interview/</a>"},{"pid":"2f22a28e864c9644a25ca7bcbae524d64954cd2a","tid":2252827,"uid":134739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2206bea9b1a3f5ea8ed55fdbf163e3aa5c9fb989","tid":2252827,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:33:36.000Z","msg":"個版權喺邊個到<br />\n應該唔難整<br />\n課金抽下skin咁應該幾好搵？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:51:11.000Z","msg":"深夜又出廢post"},{"pid":"c6e09ac2314bbb9c9da7e094f09092081b816c47","tid":2252827,"uid":57308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f22a28e864c9644a25ca7bcbae524d64954cd2a","tid":2252827,"uid":134739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2206bea9b1a3f5ea8ed55fdbf163e3aa5c9fb989","tid":2252827,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:33:36.000Z","msg":"個版權喺邊個到<br />\n應該唔難整<br />\n課金抽下skin咁應該幾好搵？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20